text: :For people of a similar name see Mickey Finn (disambiguation) or Michael Flynn (disambiguation) Michael J. Finn is an American politician who represents the 6th Hampden District in the Massachusetts House of Representatives and was member of the West Springfield City Council from 2004–2011.Massachusetts Legislature profile ==See also== * 2019–2020 Massachusetts legislature ==References== Category:People from West Springfield, Massachusetts Category:Massachusetts College of Liberal Arts alumni Category:Massachusetts Democrats Category:Living people Category:Members of the Massachusetts House of Representatives Category:Massachusetts city council members Category:21st-century American politicians Category:1970 births
